          ⚠️ Payroll Verification requires both QuickBooks and Gusto to be connected.<br>
          <span style="margin-top:0.4rem;display:block;">QBO: Connected ✅ &nbsp;|&nbsp; Gusto: Not Connected — <a href="/connect">Connect Gusto</a></span>
